There are a very limited set of functions available within the Multi-currency payment rail.

1. Quote: debit amount in selected LCU to any credit LCU
2. PayMe: request payment in LCU.
3. Account multi-currency balance
4. PayToSin: transfer global payments across currency areas via World Currency Unit (Gold).

Notes
1. Minimum cross currency area payment is one-half troy ounce or 50 WCU bits ~USD 2,500
